description:
This is my genesis piece on this platform, "Natality". The title means birth rate, which in this case is of this piece where patterns of both 2d and 3d elements are used (Zoom into the rectangles to find the 3d designs) to show an opening that is considered to be the birth of a whole new array of designs. Though a simple pattern, this tries to show a simple beginning. There are rectangles within rectangles and upon that the 3d bowl structure is placed, from afar this may seem to be a simple flat image, but the details that went into making this pattern consists of multiple layers repeated and stacked upon each other.

Technical Specifications 
Dimensions used - 4000 * 4000 pixels
Pattern Structure - Brick, Hex, Grid
Exported Image - PNG
